content.rendered:
Directed By Anurag Kashyap

Written By Nihit Bhave

Stars Taapsee Pannu(Antara Awasthi / Antara Vashisht). Pavail Gulati(Inspector Anay Anand). Himanshi Choudhary(Sheela). Saswata Chatterjee(Raja Ghosh). Rahul Bhat(Vikas Awasthi (as Rahul Bhatt)). Shaurya Duggal(Young Abhisheik). Shashwat Dwivedi(Male Nurse in Parallel Universe). Sukant Goel(Abhisheik). Medini Kelamane(Rujutha). Vidushi Mehra(Shika Vats). Al Yasaha Naim(Al Yasaha). Nassar(Dr. Sethupathi). Myra Rajpal(Avanti Vikas Awasthi). Madhurima Roy(Sara Kunder). Aarian Sawant(Young Anay). Priti Shroff(Nurse Preeti). Nidhi Singh(Bhavna). Rahul Tewari(Inspector)

Language Hindi

Producer Gaurav Bose. Ekta Kapoor. Shobha Kapoor. Lubna Khan. Sunir Kheterpal. Amit Ajit Naik. Nachiket Pantvaidya. Ruchikaa Kapoor Sheikh.

Production Cult Movies. Balaji Motion Pictures
